passwordValidation: Password must be between 12 to 36 character long contain at least one uppercase letter, one lowercase letter, one numeric digit, and one special character

content.homeH2: Dear {IP}, ip.onl is the next generation of what-is-my-ip services! With our premium experience you can quickly get information based on network or in your terminal using curl. You can also use our API to utilize our service in your own amazing platform!

apiPage.h2: Our API usage is pretty simple!
apiPage.h3: You need to generate an API key from your Dashboard

aboutUsPage.description: As a multinational conglomerate with a diverse portfolio of startups across various sectors, we recognized a significant gap in the market for reliable and cost-effective network information services. This realization led to the creation of {IPONL}, a pioneering service designed to address the shortcomings of existing providers that were either too unreliable or prohibitively expensive. Our mission with {IPONL} was to offer a solution that not only meets the high standards of reliability and affordability but also seamlessly integrates with developers' needs through a Public API. This service reflects our commitment to innovation and our dedication to solving real-world problems by leveraging our extensive experience and resources across our global operations.
